{"tid":174592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警起訴佔中三子等人妨擾罪　陳淑莊亦接通知","createTime":"2017-03-27T02:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T19:21:02.000Z","uid":48093,"like":14,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a17e21161e77af3d4e90d1e8424e56c4b0f0780a","tid":174592,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170327/photo/bkn-20170327101717657-0327_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170327102729\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170327%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170327101717657-0327_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170327102729&h=b6171fee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佔領行動於2014年9月28日凌晨正式爆發，並由金鐘蔓延至旺角、銅鑼灣等多個佔領區，期間發生大量阻街、襲警、破壞公物、阻差辦公及違反法庭禁制令等刑事罪行。據了解，發起行動的「佔中三子」發起人戴耀廷、陳健民及朱耀明，接獲警方通知將落案起訴妨擾罪。<br />\n<br />\n另外，立法會議員陳淑莊今於其facebook發貼指，今早收到警方通知落案起訴她兩年前參加佔中，她亦聽聞「佔中三子」、一些前學聯成員、佔中集會司儀邵家臻都收到通知，她將於今午立法會環境事務委員會會議後前往警署。"},{"pid":"f34d168d2875fc82db608ff6d7ddd00fe0dd95a6","tid":174592,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:31:49.000Z","msg":"777咁快開始做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181eaa8ab9087838e533edc5f68fe7d2fd5080dd","tid":174592,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:33:37.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b05dca965c0a0ecab9873566ea7eb943d3981d","tid":174592,"uid":84095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢三個仆街抵撚死啦"},{"pid":"7b10659df015c198bd7837399f4c5185d53615c0","tid":174592,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/2